===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A large [[mythical]] [[bird]] or bird-like creature that appears in both [[w:Hindu mythology|Hindu]] and [[w:Buddhist mythology|Buddhist]] [[w:mythology|mythology]]. Garuda is the son of [[Kadruva]].
# The Hindu name for the constellation [[Aquila]].

